snippet.title: Rinascita Carnevale!
snippet.description:
Plushie DJs in the house?!
Be unstoppable!
Delicacy rules!
Record the world!
Bubbles for all!
The Fool's Troupe, Salotto Open Air Gallery, Trattoria Margherita, Pioneer Association, and the Montelli family warmly invite you to a rave journey of endless celebration!
May the joy never fade—Let the Rinascita Carnevale sweep you away!
